{
  "texts": [
    "Use of this roadmap to engage collaborators and stakeholders (i.e., immunologists, clinicians and clinical researchers, assay developers, mathematical modelers, and biologists) to facilitate the collection of existing data and develop the capability to acquire new types of data as needed.",
    "for clinical decision-support.",
    "Ideally, there should be enough preliminary data such that reasonable planning could be implemented after a short period for clinical trials to demonstrate their utility.",
    "The engine of any MDT is a computational model.",
    "Depending on the application and available data, it may include mechanistic information about the relevant human biology, and it may take as input information specific to either an individual patient or a patient population."
  ]
}